highlights.text: “No Broke Boys” by Disco Lines and Tinashe has been on Viral Songs USA the longest, at 74 days straight.
Hayley Williams has the most spots on Viral Songs USA. “Kill Me” is the highest at #12.
“Keeps Me Sane” by Tyler Nance is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs USA, up 10 spots at #58.
“LV Sandals” by EsDeeKid, fakemink, and Rico Ace is the highest new entry on Viral Songs USA at #98.
